data.title: San Francisco Chronicle: "Actress Liv Ullmann, director Jan Troell pay tribute to Max von Sydow in Bay Area film series"
data.meta_description: "The focus of a six-film online retrospective, which pays tribute to the star a year after his death at age 90 and is available to stream through April 30, showcases the work in his native Sweden that forms the spine of his extraordinary career.Read the article.Watch the films.
data.text:
"The focus of a six-film online retrospective, which pays tribute to the star a year after his death at age 90 and is available to stream through April 30, showcases the work in his native Sweden that forms the spine of his extraordinary career.

Read the article.
